('fea305b0-dc45-579c-89a1-fbc0e632d0e5', 'c0215e23-91f1-4ae9-b39b-b68eff80cb98', 'I think it is ___ to travel to different countries to experience new cultures.', '我認為去不同的國家體驗新文化是很有趣的。', 'interesting', 'boring', 'dangerous', 'expensive', '字首 inter- (在...之間), 字根 est (存在), 字尾 -ing (令人...的)', 'interest (興趣) + ing (令人...的) → interesting (有趣的)'),
('c01b2a84-7403-58af-a038-2ea64e46d3c9', '4cb49395-91b8-403d-bb41-77e22ac4ae2f', 'It takes a lot of ___ to study hard.', '努力學習需要很大的意志力。', 'will', 'skill', 'luck', 'power', 'will 為單字，無詞根或詞綴。', 'will → 堅定的決心。');
